  "text": "GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links. Konami's remastered collection of the first two Suikoden role-playing games is on sale for a huge discount for Amazon Prime Day. Suikoden I \u0026 II HD Remaster's physical edition is $30 for Nintendo Switch and PS5, while the Xbox Series X edition is down to $29. Amazon's deal matches the all-time best price, which was offered by multiple retailers in early June. At the time of writing, Amazon is the only retailer with deals on the Suikoden collection this week.Suikoden I \u0026 II HD Remaster: Gate Rune \u0026 Dunan Unification Deals: Nintendo Switch -- $30 ($50)PS5 -- $30 ($50)Xbox Series X -- $29 ($50)PC (Steam) -- $30.24 ($50)PC players can take can get a very similar deal at GameSpot sister site Fanatical. Steam keys are discounted to $30.24 for the next couple of days. Suikoden I \u0026 II HD Remaster Physical Edition $30 (was $50) Amazon still lists the Nintendo Switch version as the Day One Edition, but the PS5 and Xbox Series X versions do not have \"Day One Edition\" in their names. That said, you might get the Day One Edition if you order a copy for PlayStation or Xbox. The box art has the Day One emblem, and it's possible Konami hasn't even printed standard edition copies yet.In any case, the Day One Edition comes with a few helpful in-game bonuses. Inside the box you'll find a code that unlocks immediate access to the Prosperity Orb and Fortune Orb in-game items, which double the amount of money and experience you earn from battles, respectively. You also get a bonus 57,300 Potch (in-game currency).The Orb items are acquirable in the game, but they're rare drops, so having them available immediately is a perk for players who don't want to spend as much time farming Potch and XP.The remasters of both games feature HD sprites and backgrounds, enhanced sound effects, and QOL options like auto-saving, adjustable battle speeds, and a conversation log for reviewing previous dialogue. Amazon Prime Day Gaming DealsShop PS5 Game \u0026 Accessory DealsShop Nintendo Switch Game \u0026 Accessory DealsShop Xbox Game \u0026 Accessory DealsSee PC Gaming Hardware \u0026 Accessory Deals Disclosure: GameSpot and Fanatical are both owned by Fandom. The Criterion Collection 50% Off Movie Sale - Here Are The Best Deals Little Nightmares 3 Amazon-Exclusive Mirror Edition Is Up For Preorder Lego's First Visual History For Adults Is 60% Off In Early Prime Day Deal + Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals \u0026 Preorders Links (5) Amazon Restocks Rune Factory: Guardians Of Azuma Earth Dancer Edition All Four Discontinued Donkey Kong Lego Sets Restocked At Amazon Death Stranding 2 Collector's Edition Is In Stock Ahead Of Tomorrow's Launch Donkey Kong Bananza Game \u0026 Amiibo Bundle Available At Walmart Marvel's Spider-Man Magic: The Gathering Preorders Restocked At Amazon Got a news tip or want to contact us directly? Email news@gamespot.com",
